Building:
---------

Run ./configure && make


Installation:
-------------

make install <environment>

<environment> can be one or more of the following:

prefix=PREFIX
bindir=BINDIR
dirmode=DIRMODE
filemode=FILEMODE
owner=OWNER
group=GROUP

for example:

make install bindir=/usr/local/bin filemode=555 owner=nobody

The install target supports DESTDIR.

